  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The best way to cool a very hot person is using cold water immersion, however, the&#xD;
      optimization of this technique has not been established. The goal of this study is to&#xD;
      determine differences in cooling rates among two types of cold water immersion and passive&#xD;
      cooling following immersion.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
